<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5219218>
    dc:description "Figure 15. Cnemidocarpa completa (QM G328141): A, external view; B, internal view, right side showing branchial sac cut away to display gonads. Stolonica aluta (QM G328460): C, external view of a single zooid; D, pallial wall showing gut and gonads on left side. Pyura scortea (QM G328138): E, external view. Molgula elva sp.nov. (WAM Z27525): F, detail of branchial infundibula; G, internal view showing body organs and muscualture. Scales: A, E, 0.5 cm; B–D, 0.2 cm; F, 0.5 mm; G, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5219218/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

